      },
      "lineNbr": 1652,
      "author": {
        "id": 1082465
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-09-19T16:20:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "we need to wait on the readback worker to have done its GL initialization, or we could be calling glReadPixels on a GL buffer that has not enough data allocated, which can result in segfault.",
      "parentUuid": "5190aba8_0f0b6f99",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 1652,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 1652,
        "endChar": 46
